{"tid":2306810,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［記錄香港抗爭同黑白顛倒時代嘅舞台劇］新聞小花的告白2 - 網上版本即將開放","createTime":"2020-11-30T16:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T16:11:40.000Z","uid":48124,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dea19d3f0456daf6d2698ff90dab7111d325ed33","tid":2306810,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"簡單來講，係一套令你睇完想大叫「光復香港，時代革命」嘅劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9YCKgh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9YCKgh.png&h=91c34d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為林鄭政府嘅濕鳩政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />令到呢套劇只係做咗幾場就要腰斬，如果想支持一班黃到金嘅演員同埋劇團嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以去以下連結留意佢哋稍後推出嘅網上版本：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/windmillgrasstheatre/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwindmillgrasstheatre%2F&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=48908e27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/windmillgrasstheatre/</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n係時候詳細介紹返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家最近有冇留意卓韻芝同埋梁祖堯嘅動向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />卓韻芝除咗有喺chill club經典cap圖「唔好啦」之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來佢仲幫風車草劇團做緊一套舞台劇「新聞小花的告白2- 白屋之夏」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sD0Bfo2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsD0Bfo2.jpg&h=bc422113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻睇吓由主辦單位寫嘅簡介：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「我相信的不是你所說的」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當社會動蕩﹐假新聞橫行﹐新聞工作者為揭露真相﹐可以去到幾盡?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「唯真為善」這個崇高的信念遇上考驗，究竟應該如何決擇 。誰是誰非?真假如何判斷?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好....睇完都唔知係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單來講，就係一套關於是非黑白顛倒嘅時代之下，一為記者為咗揭露秘密收押中心/再教育營「天使村」，而去追尋真相嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劇裏面有唔少場口都同過去一年香港發生嘅事息息相關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由抗爭現場黑警暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、到新屋領被捕者嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、到離地高官搞鳩「教育界」/ 剝奪新聞自由為咗提供「正確資訊」為民眾洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成套劇講緊係一個非常之沉重認真嘅題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同時代緊扣同時亦都不失令香港人共鳴嘅一啲會心微笑嘅對白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一齊睇吓觀眾睇完之後有咩感受先：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0i8CKhc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0i8CKhc.png&h=88996f63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vDpuAoS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvDpuAoS.png&h=c58e1683&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9EQBfoT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EQBfoT.png&h=2ab454b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebwwOJT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FebwwOJT.png&h=3c583514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但因為林鄭政府本身嘅濕鳩政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、加上立法會入邊成班建制派議員戇鳩鳩辦事不力，呢套劇只做咗幾場就需要被腰斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係劇團成班演員已經排咗好耐、台燈聲樣樣野都set好咗、本身劇場有限制人數之後都已經未必可以「打個和」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家突然cut咗可以話係血本無歸....<br />\n<br />\n睇吓演員之一嘅梁祖堯嬲到點<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQ7LTaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQ7LTaQ.jpg&h=48070d05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家想支持呢個劇團嘅話，又或者想一齊想再次感受呢一份屬於香港人嘅抗爭熱度同埋共鳴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以去以下連結，留意佢哋即將開賣嘅網上版本，星期六晚一齊睇片重溫呢套咁精彩嘅劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/windmillgrasstheatre/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwindmillgrasstheatre%2F&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=48908e27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/windmillgrasstheatre/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，香港人，報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望黎明好快會來臨"},{"pid":"f2707503b5dd9677dfce055fc8daa667754deeec","tid":2306810,"uid":76342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n但係原本個post講有online version <br />\n而家好似無咗段字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3d40d0523a0624b0d98db169a37d925df82d46","tid":2306810,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2707503b5dd9677dfce055fc8daa667754deeec","tid":2306810,"uid":76342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n但係原本個post講有online version <br />\n而家好似無咗段字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"應該只係有啲細節仲未確實confirm遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fdba134988ad880a4c788da8ef95719933a0d8","tid":2306810,"uid":145574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74137d75577e535e281e3f32887f9f19b30fbf0f","tid":2306810,"uid":76342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df3d40d0523a0624b0d98db169a37d925df82d46","tid":2306810,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,